Package com.gcu.agms.service.impl

Class JdbcAssignmentService

java.lang.Object
com.gcu.agms.service.impl.JdbcAssignmentService
All Implemented Interfaces:
AssignmentService
@Service("jdbcAssignmentService") @Primary public class JdbcAssignmentService extends Object implements AssignmentService
JDBC implementation of the AssignmentService interface. This service uses a database repository for gate assignment operations.
